{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-52","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam glas i vežbavao izgovor početnih slova i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da bi izgovorio <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sh</span>, lagano savijte jezik unazad i gore ka tvrdom nepcu, stvarajući širok, ali uski prolaz. Pustite vazduh da prolazi kontinuirano kroz ovaj prostor, proizvodeći blag i stabilan zvuk trenja bez zaustavljanja ili eksplozije.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sh</span> prati sufikse <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sha</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shu</span>.</p>\n<p>Nećemo da vežbamo izgovor ovih slogova, zatim koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span> u različitim tonom kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shē</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">奢</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shé</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">舌</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shě</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">舍</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shè</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">射</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-52"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception